key "breckenridge_consumption_book"

\end_inset

) or even by Maslow (who had proposed a theory of hierarchy of needs - where
 “physiological” needs are fulfilled later then social needs) is consciously
 avoided - in favour of more measurable parameters of social norms e.g.
 the classification of consumption as bandwagon or snob type
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "yamada_sombartian"

\end_inset

 - or other assessments of 
